From aeb36582baa95df88882e999c40d4e405dc57d92 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <claude@anthropic.com>
Date: Sun, 19 Jul 2026 10:52:53 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Wire frontend to real backend API and fix routing mismatches

- Fix /api -> /api/v1 prefix mismatch in all 16 lib/api.ts calls
- Add apps/web/.env.local with NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL
- Wire LoginPage/RegisterPage to real login/register endpoints,
  save tokens, add RegisterPage API-error banner
- Fix AppShell nav items pointing at nonexistent /app/* routes;
  wire real auth check, real user, real sign-out (was hardcoded
  'Jane Doe' with no route protection)
- Rewrite ChatPage.tsx to use real conversations/messages instead
  of local-only state; add lib/format.ts helper it depends on
- Rewrite KnowledgePage.tsx against real backend shapes; drop
  fabricated activity timeline, embedding-model metadata, and
  chunk browser (no backend endpoint supports listing raw chunks)
- Add services/api/.env.example and services/ai-service/.env.example
